    Package Description
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.core
    Core library of the autopia4j framework for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.impl.modular.basic
    Core library of the autopia4j basic modular implementation for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.impl.modular.dataIterative
    Core library of the autopia4j modular iterative implementation for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile
    com.autopia4j.framework.webdriver.impl.modular.dataNonIterative
    Core library of the autopia4j modular non-iterative implementation for Selenium WebDriver
    This library is designed specifically for testing web applications (desktop as well as mobile), and integrates with Selenium WebDriver, Galen, Appium and Perfecto Mobile
